This paper is about integrating logical knowledge into a deep learning system for information extraction tasks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which includes topics such as natural language processing and information retrieval. The paper also involves deep learning, which suggests cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as another likely category. The use of logical rules and constraints indicates cs.LG (Machine Learning) as a possible category. Additionally, the paper deals with structured information, which could fall under cs.DB (Databases) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
